'''Kandaas''' was the name of a cave on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Solem]].

[[Yolan Bren]] and his [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] companions tried to hide from [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] in this cave, however the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] tracked them down before they could reach it.

